Que: - Why Future method does not support non premitive data as a parameter?

Ans: -  Due to the Data Corruption, As we do not know the when Asynchronus will be runned but we have given the data to the 
        future method and in behind the scene same record has been changed by someone so process will be killed like 
        data will be overriden. that is the reason future method does not accept the non premitive data type.

Follow up question: - Above is the reson for non premitive datatype in future method how it works in schedulable?
    Ans :- 
          Future Methods are static methods. They take inputs directly as parameters. Salesforce has to instantly 
          serialize those parameters and dump them into a background system queue.

          Schedulable Classes are object-oriented. You instantiate the class as an object using the new keyword, and 
          you can pass non-primitive data into its constructor.
